                    <p>
                        As a member of a gym, you always want to get the most out of your visits to the gym. You don't want to spend
                        ages waiting for the equipment you want to use to become free. You don't want go all the way to gym to attend
                        a class that is actually full or cancelled. You want to know everything that is happening at your gym. This
                        application is here to help you with all of this.
                    </p>
