                        <li>
                            <strong>Book your class spot</strong> - Make sure you can attend the classes you want by booking your spot.
                            You do this by going into the details of a class and pressing the "Book Class" button.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>See how many people are at the gym</strong> - Make informed decisions about whether to go to gym
                            by seeing how much people are currently there. You can see this number on your welcome screen.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Be informed</strong> - You will always know what's happening at your gym. The managers can send
                            announcements informing you of what's happening. How are you informed? Either by email or by push notifications.
                            You can also view all the announcements ever made by going to the announcements page. You are also informed by email
                            if a class you have booked for has been cancelled.
                        </li>
